The paper deals with the problem of maximizing a monotone submodular set function subject to linear packing constraints, which is a well-studied problem in the area of combinatorial optimization. The paper presents an efficient combinatorial algorithm that achieves an approximation ratio, which suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
